{"tid":1825813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真中共春袋","createTime":"2020-01-15T15:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T17:04:21.000Z","uid":245713,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f33e53ea111fc7f17fd7bc64a784485b3ab9be6a","tid":1825813,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"中共春袋就只有錢，可以大幅影響中共收入既就係出口<br />\n<br />\n我地一直覺得可以影響中共出口既只有1. 關係法 同2.關稅<br />\n<br />\n但我地冇諗過可以壯大佢既對手。冇錯，就係將其他東南亞地方壯大，而呢一刻對中共世界工廠最有威脅既地方就係越南！<br />\n<br />\n一黎越南人唔太鐘意中國人，二愈越南物價比中共低好多。<br />\n<br />\n所以我呼籲黃店嘗試將made in China 既野轉成made in Vietnam。<br />\n光時都可以同越南超級/甚至試下搵big C 合作，係香港殺出一條取代品！"},{"pid":"d91422ce92b6c5e445aa36759cef6b0f5bcfdfbc","tid":1825813,"uid":245713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:18:58.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"29584f3eca074d5f4db508351347f54a98220e33","tid":1825813,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"打倒藍店，由初級生產開始"},{"pid":"592981cd5148e04757b4482476886d07fe61a239","tid":1825813,"uid":245713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"新世界工廠！"},{"pid":"3d8c58545fe544924cc3396d4aaff8142fbdfe6c","tid":1825813,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:20:07.000Z","msg":"支共快破產"},{"pid":"039f61b713b43f42ffcc53aa1d483ca91761cd01","tid":1825813,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"我要支爆"},{"pid":"0c716519f1faabab6f12eff626dbf5a2b6111b36","tid":1825813,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:20:24.000Z","msg":"Boycott China"},{"pid":"2b80b158fc3f5ca5cac1bc1a92151e8d20e44580","tid":1825813,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:20:32.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"9d4d2c525c1400b3eb7b4d1e2cf7a26ca05b58b1","tid":1825813,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{